 backend/workers/parsers/_marketfiyati.py      | 19 +++++--------------
 backend/workers/parsers/_marketfiyati_base.py |  6 +-----
 backend/workers/run_marketfiyati.py           |  2 --
 3 files changed, 6 insertions(+), 21 deletions(-)

